    Class InvertExtension

    XAML extension to invert the Value property using the current IValueInverter. Supports every System.Windows.Markup.MarkupExtension e.g., System.Windows.Data.BindingBase.

    Syntax
    public class InvertExtension : MarkupExtension
    Examples

    Provide the value locally or via data binding:

    <TextBox Text="{Invert True}" /> // returns: False
    <TextBox Text="{Invert 12}" /> // returns: -12
    <TextBox Text="{Invert {x:Static Visibility.Hidden}}" /> // returns: Visibility.Visible
    <TextBox Text="{Invert {Binding TextValue}}" />

    Value

    The Value to invert. Can everything that the provided ValueInverter can invert. The value can also be a System.Windows.Data.BindingBase or any other System.Windows.Markup.MarkupExtension that can provide the invertible value.
